1
00:01:52,208 --> 00:01:55,008
- HUH? WHAT'S THAT?

2
00:01:55,042 --> 00:01:57,842
- A STRONG DEMONIC AURA.

3
00:02:01,808 --> 00:02:03,675
[ROARS]
- HUH?

4
00:02:07,075 --> 00:02:08,142
- BE CAREFUL.

5
00:02:08,175 --> 00:02:10,075
THE EVIL IS DRAWING NEAR.

6
00:02:10,108 --> 00:02:11,675
- WHERE ARE YOU?

7
00:02:11,708 --> 00:02:13,808
COME ON AND SHOW YOURSELF.

8
00:02:13,842 --> 00:02:16,475
[GRASS RUSTLING]

9
00:02:18,142 --> 00:02:20,208
- IT'S UNDERGROUND.

10
00:02:21,608 --> 00:02:22,475
- AAH!

11
00:02:22,508 --> 00:02:25,075
[SHRIEKING]

12
00:02:27,442 --> 00:02:28,975
- UNH!

13
00:02:29,008 --> 00:02:31,008
- YUCK! WHAT IS THAT JUNK?

14
00:02:31,042 --> 00:02:32,275
IT'S MELTING THE GROUND!

15
00:02:32,308 --> 00:02:34,542
- SHIPPO!
- WHOA!

16
00:02:36,842 --> 00:02:39,142
- I'LL STOP IT!

17
00:02:39,175 --> 00:02:40,308
- TAKE THIS!

18
00:02:40,342 --> 00:02:41,975
[SHOUTING]

19
00:02:42,008 --> 00:02:43,408
- YAAH!

20
00:02:43,442 --> 00:02:45,142
- AAH!

21
00:02:45,175 --> 00:02:47,275
[ROARS]

22
00:02:47,975 --> 00:02:50,675
- IT'S OVER!

23
00:02:50,708 --> 00:02:51,642
- HANG ON!

24
00:02:51,675 --> 00:02:53,608
- HUH? WHAT NOW?

25
00:02:53,642 --> 00:02:55,342
- [GRUNTING]

26
00:02:55,375 --> 00:02:56,842
- UNH!

27
00:02:59,908 --> 00:03:02,508
- IT CAN'T FIGHT ANYMORE.

28
00:03:12,608 --> 00:03:13,542
- THANKS FOR NOTHING!

29
00:03:13,575 --> 00:03:16,908
I WAS JUST ABOUT TO
SLICE AND DICE THAT THING!

30
00:03:16,942 --> 00:03:18,475
- WELL, IT'S NO LOSS.

31
00:03:18,508 --> 00:03:20,108
IT HARDLY PUT UP A FIGHT.

32
00:03:20,142 --> 00:03:21,042
- [SIGHS]

33
00:03:21,075 --> 00:03:23,008
IT'S DISAPPOINTING
WHEN A DEMON'S APPEARANCE

34
00:03:23,042 --> 00:03:25,108
IS SO DECEIVING.

35
00:03:25,575 --> 00:03:29,175
- ALL'S WELL THAT ENDS WELL,
AND THAT'S WHAT COUNTS.

36
00:03:29,208 --> 00:03:31,908
- [PEOPLE CHEERING]

37
00:03:36,175 --> 00:03:38,808
- WHAT'S UP WITH THOSE GUYS?

38
00:03:38,842 --> 00:03:40,308
- HMM.

39
00:03:44,908 --> 00:03:48,908
OH, WE ARE FOREVER INDEBTED,
ITINERANT MONK.

40
00:03:48,942 --> 00:03:50,075
YOU SEE, THAT DEMON HAS BEEN

41
00:03:50,108 --> 00:03:52,875
RELENTLESSLY TORMENTING
OUR VILLAGE.

42
00:03:52,908 --> 00:03:54,542
- THAT DEMON HAS?

43
00:03:54,575 --> 00:03:55,408
- SHH.
- HMM?

44
00:03:55,442 --> 00:03:57,875
- OH, PLEASE LET US
REPAY YOUR KINDNESS

45
00:03:57,908 --> 00:04:01,608
WITH A SMALL BANQUET
IN YOUR HONOR.

46
00:04:01,642 --> 00:04:03,608
- [CLAMORING]

47
00:04:03,642 --> 00:04:05,942
- I WAS MERELY CARRYING
OUT MY DUTY.

48
00:04:05,975 --> 00:04:07,308
I MUST DECLINE, SIR.

49
00:04:07,342 --> 00:04:08,875
- HOW DISAPPOINTING.

50
00:04:08,908 --> 00:04:09,942
WHAT A SHAME.

51
00:04:09,975 --> 00:04:12,775
HOW WILL I EXPLAIN THIS TO
THE BEAUTIFUL YOUNG GIRLS

52
00:04:12,808 --> 00:04:15,442
OF THE VILLAGE,
WHO EAGERLY AWAIT YOU?

53
00:04:15,475 --> 00:04:18,375
- HUH?
- OH, WELL.

54
00:04:18,408 --> 00:04:19,675
- WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

55
00:04:19,708 --> 00:04:21,542
THEN AGAIN, I WOULDN'T
WANT TO BE PUNISHED

56
00:04:21,575 --> 00:04:24,142
BY THE GODS FOR
REJECTING YOUR KINDNESS.

57
00:04:24,175 --> 00:04:24,975
- HUH?

58
00:04:25,008 --> 00:04:27,008
- FUNNY HOW THE MENTION
OF YOUNG GIRLS

59
00:04:27,042 --> 00:04:28,308
CAN CHANGE HIS MIND.

60
00:04:28,342 --> 00:04:31,942
- HE'S SUCH A LECHEROUS MONK.

61
00:04:31,975 --> 00:04:34,542
- [LAUGHING]

62
00:04:36,142 --> 00:04:38,775
- "FAREWELL DAYS OF MY YOUTH."

63
00:04:50,442 --> 00:04:52,375
- THESE BEANS ARE DELICIOUS.

64
00:04:52,408 --> 00:04:54,108
- IT'S SO YUMMY!

65
00:04:54,142 --> 00:04:55,142
THEY'RE GREAT!

66
00:04:55,175 --> 00:04:57,742
IT'S BEEN A WHILE SINCE
WE'VE HAD SUCH GREAT FOOD.

67
00:04:57,775 --> 00:04:59,108
WHAT'S THE MATTER, SANGO?

68
00:04:59,142 --> 00:05:00,342
YOU HAVEN'T TOUCHED YOUR FOOD.

69
00:05:00,375 --> 00:05:04,442
- YOUR PALM SAYS THAT YOU WILL
BE BLESSED WITH MANY OFFSPRING.

70
00:05:04,475 --> 00:05:05,808
- [GASPS]

71
00:05:05,842 --> 00:05:06,642
- MY DEAR,

72
00:05:06,675 --> 00:05:09,942
WOULD YOU CONSIDER
BEARING MY CHILDREN?

73
00:05:09,975 --> 00:05:11,142
- OH, YES!

74
00:05:11,175 --> 00:05:11,842
- GAAH!

75
00:05:11,875 --> 00:05:14,775
- I'LL HAVE AS MANY AS YOU WANT.

76
00:05:14,808 --> 00:05:16,308
15 OR 16--

77
00:05:16,342 --> 00:05:18,408
YOU CHOOSE THE NUMBER.

78
00:05:18,442 --> 00:05:19,642
LET'S GET TO IT.

79
00:05:19,675 --> 00:05:20,742
- AAH!

80
00:05:20,775 --> 00:05:21,842
HELP, SANGO!

81
00:05:21,875 --> 00:05:23,208
DON'T JUST SIT THERE AND WATCH!

82
00:05:23,242 --> 00:05:24,342
DO SOMETHING!

83
00:05:24,375 --> 00:05:25,308
- HMM.

84
00:05:25,342 --> 00:05:28,308
YOU'VE FINALLY FOUND
SOMEONE WILLING AND ABLE.

85
00:05:28,342 --> 00:05:29,575
YOU HAVE MY BLESSINGS.

86
00:05:29,608 --> 00:05:32,242
- NOW, THAT'S A COLD SHOULDER.

87
00:05:32,275 --> 00:05:33,175
- RIGHT THIS WAY.

88
00:05:33,208 --> 00:05:35,908
- AFTER THE YOUNG MEN AGAIN,
ARE YOU, GRANNY?

89
00:05:35,942 --> 00:05:38,475
- OH, I MAY BE OLD,
BUT I AIN'T RUSTY.

90
00:05:38,508 --> 00:05:39,942
HA HA HA HA!

91
00:05:39,975 --> 00:05:42,542
- [LAUGHING]

92
00:05:45,742 --> 00:05:49,208
- I DIDN'T KNOW THEY HAD
FAMILY REUNIONS IN THIS ERA.

93
00:05:49,242 --> 00:05:51,575
MAKES ME ALL WARM AND FUZZY.

94
00:05:51,608 --> 00:05:53,508
- WHAT'S A FAMILY UNION?

95
00:05:53,542 --> 00:05:54,575
- HMM?

96
00:05:54,608 --> 00:05:55,575
MMM...

97
00:05:55,608 --> 00:05:56,775
IT'S WHEN PARENTS
AND GRANDPARENTS AND SIBLINGS

98
00:05:56,808 --> 00:06:01,175
ALL GET TOGETHER TO EAT
AND ENJOY EACH OTHER'S COMPANY.

99
00:06:01,208 --> 00:06:02,675
- HMM?

100
00:06:08,508 --> 00:06:09,708
ARRGH!

101
00:06:09,742 --> 00:06:12,008
THANKS, BUT NO, THANKS.

102
00:06:12,042 --> 00:06:14,042
[GROANING]

103
00:06:14,075 --> 00:06:14,775
AAH!

104
00:06:14,808 --> 00:06:15,808
- DON'T BE SO RUDE.

105
00:06:15,842 --> 00:06:18,742
BESIDES, YOU SHOULDN'T LIE
DOWN RIGHT AFTER A MEAL.

106
00:06:18,775 --> 00:06:21,542
- YEAH? SAYS WHO?

107
00:06:21,575 --> 00:06:23,142
- [SMOOCHING SOUND]

108
00:06:23,175 --> 00:06:26,075
- MMH!

109
00:06:27,742 --> 00:06:29,208
- HMM?

110
00:06:30,675 --> 00:06:32,408
- MYOGA?!

111
00:06:32,442 --> 00:06:34,108
- OHH.

112
00:06:34,142 --> 00:06:35,775
I WAS A BIT CONCERNED
ABOUT YOU,

113
00:06:35,808 --> 00:06:38,508
MASTER INUYASHA,
SO I SOUGHT YOU OUT...

114
00:06:38,542 --> 00:06:41,642
ONLY TO FIND YOU BATTLING
A FEROCIOUS CENTIPEDE.

115
00:06:41,675 --> 00:06:42,475
I'M GLAD YOU'RE SAFE.

116
00:06:42,508 --> 00:06:44,108
- FUNNY HOW YOU'RE
NOWHERE TO BE FOUND

117
00:06:44,142 --> 00:06:45,042
WHEN WE'RE IN BATTLE,

118
00:06:45,075 --> 00:06:46,108
YET YOU NEVER MISS A BEAT

119
00:06:46,142 --> 00:06:48,175
WHEN THERE'S FOOD
AND WOMEN AROUND,

120
00:06:48,208 --> 00:06:49,342
YOU LITTLE SCHEMER.

121
00:06:49,375 --> 00:06:50,442
- NOW, NOW, LET'S NOT BE CRUEL.

122
00:06:50,475 --> 00:06:53,775
- WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN ALL
THIS TIME, ANYWAY, MYOGA?

123
00:06:53,808 --> 00:06:55,142
- [CHUCKLES]

124
00:06:55,175 --> 00:06:56,342
EVEN OLD PESTS LIKE ME

125
00:06:56,375 --> 00:06:59,875
HAVE SOME BEDFELLOWS THEY'D
PREFER TO KEEP SECRET, YOU KNOW.

126
00:06:59,908 --> 00:07:02,442
[LAUGHING]

127
00:07:04,442 --> 00:07:05,775
- ARRGH.

128
00:07:05,808 --> 00:07:08,475
DEFINITELY A CREEPY CRAWLER.

129
00:07:08,508 --> 00:07:09,242
UNH!

130
00:07:09,275 --> 00:07:11,008
- OOH, OOH, AH, AH, AH!
HOT, HOT!

131
00:07:11,042 --> 00:07:12,475
HOTTER THAN HOT!
OOH, OOH!

132
00:07:12,508 --> 00:07:15,108
[WOLF HOWLING]

133
00:07:25,775 --> 00:07:27,042
- [SNORES]

134
00:07:27,075 --> 00:07:28,242
OHH...

135
00:07:28,275 --> 00:07:30,775
I COULDN'T EAT ANOTHER BITE.

136
00:07:30,808 --> 00:07:31,975
AH...

137
00:07:32,008 --> 00:07:34,008
AHH.

138
00:07:34,042 --> 00:07:34,942
[SNORING]

139
00:07:34,975 --> 00:07:37,142
[BOING BOING]

140
00:07:37,175 --> 00:07:39,008
[GRUNTING]

141
00:07:39,042 --> 00:07:41,575
[PANTING]

142
00:07:42,275 --> 00:07:43,775
SILENTLY, STEALTHILY,

143
00:07:43,808 --> 00:07:45,908
HE SNEAKS THROUGH THE NIGHT.

144
00:07:45,942 --> 00:07:47,408
HA HA.

145
00:07:51,708 --> 00:07:54,308
- [FOOTSTEPS]

146
00:08:01,342 --> 00:08:03,142
- A GHOST.

147
00:08:05,475 --> 00:08:07,042
I'VE HEARD OF SPIRITS
OF CHILDREN

148
00:08:07,075 --> 00:08:10,608
THAT LINGER ON IN OLD MANSIONS
AFTER THEIR PASSING.

149
00:08:10,642 --> 00:08:13,475
THIS MUST BE ONE SUCH PHANTOM.

150
00:08:18,742 --> 00:08:20,008
HMM.

151
00:08:20,042 --> 00:08:21,475
YAAAAH!

152
00:08:21,508 --> 00:08:22,908
ARRGH!

153
00:08:22,942 --> 00:08:23,775
MMH!

154
00:08:23,808 --> 00:08:25,042
WHO ARE YOU?

155
00:08:25,075 --> 00:08:26,242
- MMM.

156
00:08:26,275 --> 00:08:27,475
WEE WEE.

157
00:08:27,508 --> 00:08:29,175
- NO! NOT HERE!

158
00:08:29,208 --> 00:08:30,175
- GOT TO GO.

159
00:08:30,208 --> 00:08:31,042
- JUST WAIT!

160
00:08:31,075 --> 00:08:32,842
THIS ISN'T THE TOILET!

161
00:08:32,875 --> 00:08:35,842
THAT'S A BOY.

162
00:08:35,875 --> 00:08:38,408
[TINKLING]

163
00:08:42,242 --> 00:08:43,208
- [SIGHS]

164
00:08:43,242 --> 00:08:45,175
IF I'M GOING TO BE
AWAKE AT THIS HOUR,

165
00:08:45,208 --> 00:08:49,308
I CAN THINK OF OTHER THINGS
I'D RATHER BE DOING.

166
00:08:49,342 --> 00:08:51,675
- [GROANS]

167
00:08:51,708 --> 00:08:54,308
[OWL HOOTING]

168
00:08:58,475 --> 00:09:01,075
- [FOOTSTEPS]

169
00:09:05,742 --> 00:09:07,208
- MMM.

170
00:09:14,942 --> 00:09:16,942
YOU HAVE TO PEE AGAIN,
I SUPPOSE.

171
00:09:16,975 --> 00:09:20,875
BE A GOOD BOY AND GO
BY YOURSELF THIS TIME, OK?

172
00:09:22,875 --> 00:09:24,842
[GROANS]

173
00:09:24,875 --> 00:09:26,742
HUH?

174
00:09:26,775 --> 00:09:28,208
HUH?

175
00:09:30,708 --> 00:09:32,242
SANGO.

176
00:09:32,275 --> 00:09:33,508
UH, UH...

177
00:09:33,542 --> 00:09:36,508
DO YOU KNOW WHAT TIME IT IS?

178
00:09:36,542 --> 00:09:37,375
WHAT LUCK!

179
00:09:37,408 --> 00:09:40,208
SHE'S FINALLY COME
SNEAKING INTO MY BED.

180
00:09:40,242 --> 00:09:41,375
LIE DOWN.

181
00:09:41,408 --> 00:09:43,875
COME JOIN ME.

182
00:09:45,708 --> 00:09:47,175
HUH?

183
00:09:47,208 --> 00:09:48,642
AAH!

184
00:09:50,342 --> 00:09:51,775
UNH!

185
00:09:52,475 --> 00:09:53,408
AW, COME ON!

186
00:09:53,442 --> 00:09:56,508
DON'T TELL ME YOU'RE STILL
ANGRY ABOUT EARLIER!

187
00:09:56,542 --> 00:09:57,908
AAH, UNH!

188
00:09:57,942 --> 00:09:59,275
UHH...

189
00:09:59,308 --> 00:10:00,642
AAH! AAH!

190
00:10:00,675 --> 00:10:03,242
THE OLD WOMAN WAS JUST JOKING!

191
00:10:03,275 --> 00:10:04,208
AAH!

192
00:10:04,242 --> 00:10:06,342
[CRASH]

193
00:10:06,375 --> 00:10:10,542
- OH, MAN, WHAT'S ALL THIS
RUCKUS ABOUT OUT HERE?

194
00:10:10,575 --> 00:10:11,408
HUH?

195
00:10:11,442 --> 00:10:13,375
- SANGO, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO BE SO ANGRY!

196
00:10:13,408 --> 00:10:15,908
COME ON, I'M TELLING
THE TRUTH!

197
00:10:15,942 --> 00:10:16,942
AIEE!

198
00:10:16,975 --> 00:10:18,708
UNH! YAAH!

199
00:10:18,742 --> 00:10:19,908
UH, UH!

200
00:10:19,942 --> 00:10:22,375
[WHIMPERING]

201
00:10:22,408 --> 00:10:25,175
- [BREATHING SHALLOWLY]

202
00:10:26,642 --> 00:10:28,108
- UHH...

203
00:10:28,142 --> 00:10:31,008
SHE'S ATTACKING ME IN HER SLEEP.

204
00:10:31,042 --> 00:10:32,342
- [YAWNS]

205
00:10:32,375 --> 00:10:37,108
CAN'T YOU TWO KEEP YOUR LITTLE
SQUABBLES A BIT QUIETER?

206
00:10:37,142 --> 00:10:38,142
- WAIT!

207
00:10:38,175 --> 00:10:39,075
- HUH?

208
00:10:39,108 --> 00:10:39,942
- [GROANS]

209
00:10:39,975 --> 00:10:44,242
- SANGO IS POSSESSED
BY SOMETHING!

210
00:10:44,275 --> 00:10:46,508
- SANGO, WAKE UP!

211
00:10:46,542 --> 00:10:48,308
- UNH!

212
00:10:48,342 --> 00:10:49,108
- AAH!

213
00:10:49,142 --> 00:10:51,008
- STOP IT, SANGO!

214
00:10:51,042 --> 00:10:53,542
- UHH!

215
00:10:53,575 --> 00:10:55,008
- UNH.
- SANGO!

216
00:10:55,042 --> 00:10:57,975
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

217
00:10:58,008 --> 00:10:58,975
HUH?

218
00:10:59,008 --> 00:11:00,308
AAH!

219
00:11:00,342 --> 00:11:03,442
MMH!
- ARRGH...

220
00:11:03,475 --> 00:11:04,375
HMM?

221
00:11:04,408 --> 00:11:05,942
- UH...

222
00:11:05,975 --> 00:11:07,342
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

223
00:11:07,375 --> 00:11:09,108
WHAT AM I DOING HERE?

224
00:11:09,142 --> 00:11:09,775
HUH?

225
00:11:09,808 --> 00:11:11,675
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU, MIROKU?

226
00:11:11,708 --> 00:11:12,375
- WOW.

227
00:11:12,408 --> 00:11:14,242
SHE EVEN SLAPS HIM IN HER SLEEP.

228
00:11:14,275 --> 00:11:18,208
- SOMEONE BEWITCHED SANGO
RIGHT UNDER OUR NOSES.

229
00:11:18,242 --> 00:11:21,342
- UH, I DON'T REMEMBER A THING.

230
00:11:21,375 --> 00:11:22,108
- THAT'S STRANGE.

231
00:11:22,142 --> 00:11:23,942
WHO WOULD DO THAT
TO HER, THOUGH?

232
00:11:23,975 --> 00:11:25,108
- I DON'T HAVE ANY IDEA,

233
00:11:25,142 --> 00:11:28,142
BUT I DON'T SENSE ANY
EVIL AROUND THIS PLACE.

234
00:11:28,175 --> 00:11:29,508
- ARE YOU CERTAIN?

235
00:11:29,542 --> 00:11:30,308
- HUH?

236
00:11:30,342 --> 00:11:31,908
MYOGA, WHEN DID YOU
JUMP ON MIROKU?

237
00:11:31,942 --> 00:11:34,742
- ARE YOU SURE YOU DON'T
SENSE ANYTHING SUSPICIOUS?

238
00:11:34,775 --> 00:11:37,075
- ARE YOU HIDING
SOMETHING FROM US?

239
00:11:37,108 --> 00:11:39,708
- I, UH, NOT ESPECIALLY, NO.

240
00:11:39,742 --> 00:11:41,042
- HMM. WAIT A MINUTE.

241
00:11:41,075 --> 00:11:41,942
A LONG TIME AGO,

242
00:11:41,975 --> 00:11:43,275
MY FATHER TOLD ME ABOUT DEMONS

243
00:11:43,308 --> 00:11:46,742
WHO ONLY REALIZE THEIR
TRUE POWER AFTER DEATH.

244
00:11:46,775 --> 00:11:48,775
- THEY'RE POWERFUL AFTER DEATH?

245
00:11:48,808 --> 00:11:52,075
- THE MOST RECENT DEMON
WE DESTROYED WAS...

246
00:11:52,108 --> 00:11:53,142
- [GASPS]

247
00:11:53,175 --> 00:11:53,975
- HUH?

248
00:11:54,008 --> 00:11:55,075
YOU MEAN, THAT GIANT CENTIPEDE

249
00:11:55,108 --> 00:11:57,742
THAT WAS SO WEAK IS WHAT
POSSESSED SANGO?

250
00:11:57,775 --> 00:12:00,442
- YOU'D BETTER SEAL ITS
POWERS UP ONE MORE TIME,

251
00:12:00,475 --> 00:12:01,442
JUST IN CASE.

252
00:12:01,475 --> 00:12:03,142
- [WHIMPERING]

253
00:12:03,175 --> 00:12:05,742
- [GRUNTING]

254
00:12:07,642 --> 00:12:10,575
- HEY, WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU, MYOGA?

255
00:12:10,608 --> 00:12:11,575
- NOTHING.

256
00:12:11,608 --> 00:12:13,242
NOTHING AT ALL!

257
00:12:19,475 --> 00:12:22,042
- [GRUNTING]

258
00:12:34,242 --> 00:12:35,575
- IT'S JUST A CARCASS.

259
00:12:35,608 --> 00:12:37,908
- WELL, NOTHING
SUSPICIOUS ABOUT IT.

260
00:12:37,942 --> 00:12:40,742
- I THINK I'D BETTER
SEAL IT WITH ANOTHER SUTRA,

261
00:12:40,775 --> 00:12:43,575
JUST TO BE ON THE SAFE SIDE.

262
00:12:45,542 --> 00:12:47,008
- OOH.

263
00:12:47,342 --> 00:12:50,308
KAGOME, YOU DON'T HAVE
ANY LUCK WITH MEN.

264
00:12:50,342 --> 00:12:51,242
- OH, I DON'T?

265
00:12:51,275 --> 00:12:53,042
- YOU WON'T FIND
PEACE OR HAPPINESS

266
00:12:53,075 --> 00:12:55,875
UNLESS YOU LEAVE
YOUR CURRENT MAN.

267
00:12:55,908 --> 00:12:56,975
- HUH?

268
00:12:57,008 --> 00:12:59,808
- WHAT ABOUT YOU, SANGO?

269
00:12:59,842 --> 00:13:01,408
LET'S SEE.

270
00:13:01,442 --> 00:13:02,175
HMM.

271
00:13:02,208 --> 00:13:04,342
YOUR LUCK WITH MEN IS NO BETTER.

272
00:13:04,375 --> 00:13:06,108
YOU'D BEST FORGET ABOUT HIM.

273
00:13:06,142 --> 00:13:07,842
HE'S TOO MUCH OF A WOMANIZER.

274
00:13:07,875 --> 00:13:11,442
- YOUR PALM READING IS RIGHT
ON THE MARK, MYOGA.

275
00:13:11,475 --> 00:13:13,208
- YOU REALLY THINK SO?

276
00:13:13,242 --> 00:13:14,342
- HUH?

277
00:13:14,375 --> 00:13:15,175
WHAT?

278
00:13:15,208 --> 00:13:17,375
ARE YOU GUYS BURYING
THE DEMON ALREADY?

279
00:13:17,408 --> 00:13:18,808
[GROWLING]

280
00:13:18,842 --> 00:13:20,942
- NO, WE'RE NOT FINISHED YET.

281
00:13:20,975 --> 00:13:23,308
GET UP HERE AND HELP, MIROKU!

282
00:13:24,742 --> 00:13:25,742
- HRRM.

283
00:13:25,775 --> 00:13:26,442
- HUH?

284
00:13:26,475 --> 00:13:28,842
- I WON'T FORGIVE YOU FOR THIS!

285
00:13:28,875 --> 00:13:29,808
- AAH!

286
00:13:29,842 --> 00:13:30,642
- WHAT?

287
00:13:30,675 --> 00:13:31,708
- AAH!
- UNH!

288
00:13:31,742 --> 00:13:35,042
WHAT ARE YOU DOING--
IS THIS SOME SORT OF PAYBACK?!

289
00:13:35,075 --> 00:13:38,008
- YOU HAVE FINALLY
REVEALED YOUR TRUE SELF,

290
00:13:38,042 --> 00:13:39,908
YOU LECHEROUS MONK!

291
00:13:39,942 --> 00:13:41,042
- UNH! AAH!

292
00:13:41,075 --> 00:13:44,275
I DIDN'T REALLY THINK YOU WERE
THAT TYPE OF MAN, MIROKU.

293
00:13:44,308 --> 00:13:45,542
I WAS WRONG ABOUT YOU.

294
00:13:45,575 --> 00:13:47,808
- AND I WAS RIGHT ALL ALONG.

295
00:13:47,842 --> 00:13:49,408
- I THINK YOU'RE BOTH WRONG.

296
00:13:49,442 --> 00:13:50,675
THE SPIRIT OF THE CENTIPEDE

297
00:13:50,708 --> 00:13:53,542
MUST HAVE POSSESSED
MIROKU THIS TIME.

298
00:13:53,575 --> 00:13:54,508
- THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE.

299
00:13:54,542 --> 00:13:57,475
IT WOULD TAKE A LOT OF
POWER TO POSSESS MIROKU,

300
00:13:57,508 --> 00:13:59,142
AND I DON'T SENSE THAT.

301
00:13:59,175 --> 00:14:01,675
- UNH!

302
00:14:01,708 --> 00:14:02,608
AAH!

303
00:14:02,642 --> 00:14:04,642
[GROWLS]

304
00:14:04,675 --> 00:14:05,908
- AAH!

305
00:14:05,942 --> 00:14:06,942
- HIDE, SHIPPO!

306
00:14:06,975 --> 00:14:07,975
YOU MUST RUN TO SAFETY!

307
00:14:08,008 --> 00:14:09,742
- I FIGURED THAT MUCH OUT.

308
00:14:09,775 --> 00:14:10,742
WHOA!

309
00:14:10,775 --> 00:14:11,508
- UNH!

310
00:14:11,542 --> 00:14:14,208
YOU WON'T ESCAPE, YOU WRETCH!

311
00:14:14,242 --> 00:14:16,608
- WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

312
00:14:18,042 --> 00:14:19,742
- ARRGH!

313
00:14:19,775 --> 00:14:21,208
UNH!

314
00:14:21,975 --> 00:14:22,775
UHH.

315
00:14:22,808 --> 00:14:24,008
THIS BODY IS INADEQUATE,

316
00:14:24,042 --> 00:14:27,208
IF EVEN THAT YOUNG CHILD
CAN OUTRUN ME.

317
00:14:27,242 --> 00:14:29,075
- WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR VOICE?

318
00:14:29,108 --> 00:14:30,342
WHY ARE YOU TALKING LIKE THAT?

319
00:14:30,375 --> 00:14:32,675
- SEE? I TOLD YOU
HE WAS POSSESSED.

320
00:14:32,708 --> 00:14:34,142
- WHY, YOU...

321
00:14:34,175 --> 00:14:35,208
[BOING BOING]

322
00:14:35,242 --> 00:14:36,508
- UNH...UMM.

323
00:14:36,542 --> 00:14:38,308
- HMM?

324
00:14:38,342 --> 00:14:39,808
- UNH, UNH.

325
00:14:39,842 --> 00:14:42,842
WHAT ON EARTH HAPPENED TO ME?

326
00:14:42,875 --> 00:14:44,342
- OH!

327
00:14:45,075 --> 00:14:45,908
HEY, MIROKU,

328
00:14:45,942 --> 00:14:48,675
HAVE YOU RETURNED
TO THE OLD YOU AGAIN?

329
00:14:48,708 --> 00:14:49,542
- OH!

330
00:14:49,575 --> 00:14:53,508
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

331
00:14:53,542 --> 00:14:54,575
- THERE'S YOUR ANSWER!

332
00:14:54,608 --> 00:14:58,175
HE HAS DEFINITELY RETURNED
TO HIS OLD SELF, INUYASHA!

333
00:14:58,208 --> 00:15:01,175
- YEP, THAT'S FOR SURE.

334
00:15:01,208 --> 00:15:02,075
HMM? HANG ON.

335
00:15:02,108 --> 00:15:05,108
THERE'S SOMETHING EVIL
COMING THIS WAY.

336
00:15:05,142 --> 00:15:06,042
- HUH?

337
00:15:06,075 --> 00:15:08,542
[RUMBLING]

338
00:15:08,575 --> 00:15:10,275
- AAH!

339
00:15:10,308 --> 00:15:12,242
- [DEMON ROARING]

340
00:15:12,275 --> 00:15:13,342
- WHAT IS THAT?

341
00:15:13,375 --> 00:15:15,208
- DO YOU THINK IT COULD BE
THE OTHER CENTIPEDE'S MATE?

342
00:15:15,242 --> 00:15:18,008
- MAYBE THIS IS THE ONE
THAT POSSESSED US.

343
00:15:18,042 --> 00:15:20,108
- [DEMON ROARING]

344
00:15:20,142 --> 00:15:21,608
- AAH!

345
00:15:23,108 --> 00:15:25,075
- AAH!

346
00:15:25,108 --> 00:15:26,242
- BE CAREFUL!

347
00:15:26,275 --> 00:15:28,575
THAT STUFF'S ACID!

348
00:15:28,608 --> 00:15:30,008
- STAY HERE.

349
00:15:30,042 --> 00:15:32,108
ARRGH!

350
00:15:32,142 --> 00:15:33,808
TAKE THIS!

351
00:15:35,008 --> 00:15:37,542
WIND SCAR!

352
00:15:39,875 --> 00:15:42,575
- [DEMON SHRIEKING]

353
00:15:53,675 --> 00:15:55,142
- HUH.

354
00:15:56,542 --> 00:15:57,675
UNH.

355
00:15:57,708 --> 00:15:58,708
- AH!

356
00:15:58,742 --> 00:16:01,675
- THAT'S THE END OF ANOTHER
TROUBLESOME CENTIPEDE.

357
00:16:01,708 --> 00:16:05,042
- LOOKS LIKE I'D BETTER
SEAL UP ITS POWERS.

358
00:16:05,075 --> 00:16:07,842
[BOING BOING BOING]

359
00:16:11,875 --> 00:16:14,475
THIS PUTS AN END TO THIS AFFAIR.

360
00:16:14,508 --> 00:16:16,908
- [SIGHS]

361
00:16:16,942 --> 00:16:18,442
HRRM...

362
00:16:29,124 --> 00:16:32,657
- [SIGHS]

363
00:16:32,690 --> 00:16:35,024
HRRM...

364
00:16:35,057 --> 00:16:37,624
- [LAUGHING]

365
00:16:40,690 --> 00:16:42,590
- WHAT'S HIS PROBLEM?

366
00:16:42,624 --> 00:16:44,857
- INUYASHA?

367
00:16:44,890 --> 00:16:46,057
- HMM?

368
00:16:46,090 --> 00:16:47,090
- ARRGH.

369
00:16:47,124 --> 00:16:48,490
- AAH!

370
00:16:48,524 --> 00:16:49,290
- HUH?

371
00:16:49,324 --> 00:16:50,590
- COME BACK HERE!

372
00:16:50,624 --> 00:16:53,357
YOU'LL NEVER ESCAPE ME!

373
00:16:53,390 --> 00:16:56,257
- DON'T TELL ME HE'S
POSSESSED NOW.

374
00:16:56,290 --> 00:16:57,657
- WATCH HOW HE'S RUNNING.

375
00:16:57,690 --> 00:16:59,657
HE KIND OF LOOKS LIKE A FLEA.

376
00:16:59,690 --> 00:17:00,990
- LIKE A FLEA?

377
00:17:01,024 --> 00:17:02,290
- I'LL GET YOU!

378
00:17:02,324 --> 00:17:03,290
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

379
00:17:03,324 --> 00:17:05,390
NOW INUYASHA'S GONE CRAZY.

380
00:17:05,424 --> 00:17:06,690
- I'M COMING, MYOGA!

381
00:17:06,724 --> 00:17:08,624
- INUYASHA'S CALLING YOU.

382
00:17:08,657 --> 00:17:11,357
- THAT'S NOT MASTER INUYASHA.

383
00:17:11,390 --> 00:17:12,057
- WHAT?

384
00:17:12,090 --> 00:17:15,224
- YOU'LL NEVER GET AWAY FROM ME!

385
00:17:15,257 --> 00:17:17,357
- [GRUNTING]

386
00:17:17,390 --> 00:17:20,190
- UHH...WHOA!

387
00:17:20,224 --> 00:17:21,757
WHOA!

388
00:17:21,790 --> 00:17:23,224
UHH!

389
00:17:26,057 --> 00:17:29,024
IS THAT YOU, INUYASHA?

390
00:17:29,057 --> 00:17:29,890
- [SIGHS]

391
00:17:29,924 --> 00:17:31,457
DON'T THINK THAT YOU
CAN ESCAPE FROM ME,

392
00:17:31,490 --> 00:17:33,257
YOU NAUGHTY LITTLE RASCAL.

393
00:17:33,290 --> 00:17:35,290
I'M ALL YOURS FOR THE TAKING,

394
00:17:35,324 --> 00:17:37,124
MY SWEET FOXY DARLING.

395
00:17:37,157 --> 00:17:39,657
- INUYASHA, SNAP OUT OF IT!

396
00:17:39,690 --> 00:17:41,857
- WE'RE MEANT FOR EACH OTHER.

397
00:17:41,890 --> 00:17:43,024
- [SIGHS]

398
00:17:43,057 --> 00:17:44,424
- EEEK!

399
00:17:44,457 --> 00:17:45,524
OOH!

400
00:17:45,557 --> 00:17:48,824
WHAT ABOUT MY DREAMS OF
FALLING IN LOVE WITH A WOMAN,

401
00:17:48,857 --> 00:17:51,824
NOT A POSSESSED
MALE HALF-DEMON?

402
00:17:51,857 --> 00:17:52,724
OOH!

403
00:17:52,757 --> 00:17:54,057
- [PANTING]

404
00:17:54,090 --> 00:17:56,157
- INUYASHA, SIT, BOY!

405
00:17:56,190 --> 00:17:57,657
- UNH!

406
00:17:58,857 --> 00:18:00,324
- OHH!

407
00:18:00,357 --> 00:18:01,090
- ARRGH!

408
00:18:01,124 --> 00:18:02,824
WHAT DID YOU DO
THAT FOR, KAGOME?

409
00:18:02,857 --> 00:18:03,924
- THANK GOODNESS.

410
00:18:03,957 --> 00:18:05,690
YOU'RE BACK TO NORMAL AGAIN.

411
00:18:05,724 --> 00:18:08,290
- [GRUNTING]

412
00:18:08,924 --> 00:18:10,924
- DID I DO SOMETHING WRONG?

413
00:18:10,957 --> 00:18:13,490
- WOULD YOU GET OFF ME,
YOU RABID DOG?!

414
00:18:13,524 --> 00:18:14,757
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!

415
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:19,157
- INUYASHA, WHAT DO YOU
HAVE THERE IN YOUR HAND?

416
00:18:19,190 --> 00:18:20,990
- HMM?

417
00:18:21,024 --> 00:18:22,690
OH.

418
00:18:22,724 --> 00:18:23,457
HMM.

419
00:18:23,490 --> 00:18:24,557
- PLEASE RELEASE ME!

420
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:25,590
- IT'S MYOGA!

421
00:18:25,624 --> 00:18:28,424
- LET ME GO, MASTER INUYASHA,
I BEG YOU!

422
00:18:28,457 --> 00:18:29,790
- UNH!

423
00:18:29,824 --> 00:18:34,090
KAGOME, IT'S A FLEA--
AN UNFAMILIAR FLEA!

424
00:18:34,124 --> 00:18:35,057
- HE'S RIGHT.

425
00:18:35,090 --> 00:18:37,557
- IT CAME OUT FROM
INUYASHA'S BODY.

426
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:39,190
- I'LL NEVER ASK ANOTHER FAVOR.

427
00:18:39,224 --> 00:18:40,690
JUST LET ME GO!

428
00:18:40,724 --> 00:18:44,290
- MYOGA, THIS IS THE END
OF THE LINE FOR YOU.

429
00:18:44,324 --> 00:18:48,724
I'M TELLING YOU, YOU CANNOT
GET AWAY THIS TIME.

430
00:18:48,757 --> 00:18:49,790
- HUH?
- HUH?

431
00:18:49,824 --> 00:18:51,157
UH, EXCUSE ME.

432
00:18:51,190 --> 00:18:52,790
WHO ARE YOU?

433
00:18:52,824 --> 00:18:54,890
- [GROANING]

434
00:18:55,657 --> 00:18:57,457
- [LAUGHING]

435
00:18:57,490 --> 00:18:58,557
OH, DEAR.

436
00:18:58,590 --> 00:18:59,990
HOW RUDE OF ME.

437
00:19:00,024 --> 00:19:01,590
MY NAME IS SHOGA,

438
00:19:01,624 --> 00:19:03,290
AND ACCORDING TO OUR
PARENTS' WISHES,

439
00:19:03,324 --> 00:19:05,824
MYOGA AND I ARE
BETROTHED TO BE WED.

440
00:19:05,857 --> 00:19:07,690
- NOT TRUE, NOT TRUE!

441
00:19:07,724 --> 00:19:09,390
- YOU BE QUIET!

442
00:19:09,424 --> 00:19:11,724
- YES'M.
- HMM?

443
00:19:11,757 --> 00:19:14,224
- OLD LADY SHOGA?

444
00:19:14,257 --> 00:19:15,857
- DON'T CALL HER OLD.

445
00:19:15,890 --> 00:19:17,524
- NO INSULT TAKEN.

446
00:19:17,557 --> 00:19:18,990
WHEN A FLEA REACHES MY AGE,

447
00:19:19,024 --> 00:19:22,057
SHE WANTS TO SETTLE DOWN
AND HAVE A FAMILY,

448
00:19:22,090 --> 00:19:24,857
BUT YOU KNOW MY MYOGA HERE.

449
00:19:24,890 --> 00:19:26,057
[CRYING]

450
00:19:26,090 --> 00:19:29,224
HE'S ALWAYS BEEN
SUCH A WOMANIZER.

451
00:19:29,257 --> 00:19:31,657
WHENEVER THERE'S
A HANDSOME WOMAN AROUND,

452
00:19:31,690 --> 00:19:33,324
HE STEALS OUT TO FLIRT WITH HER

453
00:19:33,357 --> 00:19:36,224
WITHOUT A WORD OF
APOLOGY TO ME...

454
00:19:36,257 --> 00:19:38,657
AND LEAVES NARY A CLUE
TO TRACK HIM DOWN,

455
00:19:38,690 --> 00:19:41,890
AND I'M LEFT HELPLESS
TO AWAIT HIS RETURN.

456
00:19:41,924 --> 00:19:44,124
THIS TIME I HUNTED HIM DOWN,

457
00:19:44,157 --> 00:19:45,857
SWEARING TO LUG HIM BACK HOME

458
00:19:45,890 --> 00:19:49,090
EVEN IF I NEEDED TO USE
A LITTLE FORCE.

459
00:19:49,124 --> 00:19:50,490
- [YELLING]

460
00:19:50,524 --> 00:19:52,524
- SCARY.
- THE DREAM IS OVER!

461
00:19:52,557 --> 00:19:54,724
- MYOGA, ARE YOU PREPARED?

462
00:19:54,757 --> 00:19:56,424
- NO. HELP!

463
00:19:56,457 --> 00:19:59,324
RELEASE ME, MASTER INUYASHA!

464
00:19:59,357 --> 00:20:00,490
- NO CAN DO.

465
00:20:00,524 --> 00:20:01,990
- WHY? TELL ME WHY!

466
00:20:02,024 --> 00:20:04,390
- YOU KNEW THAT
OLD LADY SHOGA WAS THE ONE

467
00:20:04,424 --> 00:20:07,257
WHO BEWITCHED US
ALL ALONG, MYOGA.

468
00:20:07,290 --> 00:20:08,257
- OH!

469
00:20:08,290 --> 00:20:09,424
HRRM!

470
00:20:09,457 --> 00:20:10,324
- PLEASE!

471
00:20:10,357 --> 00:20:11,724
SURELY YOU WOULDN'T
ROB AN INNOCENT FELLOW

472
00:20:11,757 --> 00:20:13,290
OF HIS PRECIOUS YOUTH.

473
00:20:13,324 --> 00:20:15,090
- PRECIOUS YOUTH, MY FEET!

474
00:20:15,124 --> 00:20:16,324
I'LL STRAP YOU TO MY BACK

475
00:20:16,357 --> 00:20:19,124
IF THAT'S WHAT IT TAKES
TO GET YOU HOME!

476
00:20:19,157 --> 00:20:19,857
- GOOD PLAN.

477
00:20:19,890 --> 00:20:21,657
- NOW, NOW, OLD LADY SHOGA,

478
00:20:21,690 --> 00:20:24,124
I THINK YOU SHOULD
FORGIVE HIM, HMM?

479
00:20:24,157 --> 00:20:25,124
- YEAH. HE'S RIGHT.

480
00:20:25,157 --> 00:20:27,990
INSTEAD OF TAKING MYOGA'S
FREEDOM AWAY FROM HIM,

481
00:20:28,024 --> 00:20:30,757
WHY NOT STAY HERE
AND GET MARRIED?

482
00:20:30,790 --> 00:20:32,190
- UH-UH-UHH!

483
00:20:32,224 --> 00:20:34,290
GET MARRIED?!

484
00:20:34,324 --> 00:20:35,224
[CRYING]

485
00:20:35,257 --> 00:20:38,257
- AND THEN YOU CAN
START A HOME TOGETHER.

486
00:20:38,290 --> 00:20:40,757
- [SOBBING]

487
00:20:40,790 --> 00:20:41,790
- SHE'S EMBARRASSED.

488
00:20:41,824 --> 00:20:44,824
- A FEMALE'S STILL A FEMALE,
EVEN IF SHE'S A FLEA.

489
00:20:44,857 --> 00:20:46,957
- WE CAN EVEN ASK
THE HEADMAN OF THE VILLAGE

490
00:20:46,990 --> 00:20:48,057
TO BE THE GO-BETWEEN.

491
00:20:48,090 --> 00:20:50,190
- THERE'S NO NEED
FOR THE HEADMAN!

492
00:20:50,224 --> 00:20:51,057
PLEASE, PLEASE!

493
00:20:51,090 --> 00:20:53,490
- MYOGA DOESN'T SEEM
PLEASED ABOUT THIS.

494
00:20:53,524 --> 00:20:55,490
- HE'LL JUST HAVE
TO RESIGN HIMSELF.

495
00:20:55,524 --> 00:20:59,124
- YOU WILL MAKE A FINE
COUPLE OF FLEAS.

496
00:20:59,157 --> 00:21:00,690
- KILL WE NOW.

497
00:21:00,724 --> 00:21:03,290
- [WEEPING]

498
00:21:09,924 --> 00:21:12,324
- [APPLAUSE]

499
00:21:12,357 --> 00:21:18,057
- MYOGA, AT LAST WE
ARE FLEA AND WIFE.

500
00:21:18,090 --> 00:21:20,057
DON'T BE SO SHY, DEAREST.

501
00:21:20,090 --> 00:21:21,424
[GIGGLING]

502
00:21:21,457 --> 00:21:24,724
YOU COULD AT LEAST
SAY YOU LOVE ME.

503
00:21:26,424 --> 00:21:28,390
HUH?

504
00:21:28,424 --> 00:21:29,524
MYOGA?

505
00:21:29,557 --> 00:21:30,490
HMM?

506
00:21:30,524 --> 00:21:31,757
AAAH!

507
00:21:31,790 --> 00:21:32,857
- HEY, WHAT'S WRONG?

508
00:21:32,890 --> 00:21:34,157
- DID SOMETHING HAPPEN?

509
00:21:34,190 --> 00:21:35,124
- SHOGA?

510
00:21:35,157 --> 00:21:36,590
- WHAT'S THE MATTER?

511
00:21:36,624 --> 00:21:38,024
- THIS ISN'T MYOGA.

512
00:21:38,057 --> 00:21:41,590
HE SWITCHED PLACES
WITH SOME STRANGE FLEA.

513
00:21:41,624 --> 00:21:43,024
- AAH!

514
00:21:43,057 --> 00:21:46,657
- THAT MYOGA--HE RAN AWAY!

515
00:21:46,690 --> 00:21:47,657
- RUN, RUN!

516
00:21:47,690 --> 00:21:50,490
RUN TO THE END
OF THE EARTH, PLEASE!

517
00:21:50,524 --> 00:21:51,990
- [YOWLS]

518
00:21:52,024 --> 00:21:54,224
- WHY, THAT OLD GEEZER!

519
00:21:54,257 --> 00:21:55,990
GET BACK HERE!

520
00:21:56,024 --> 00:21:56,824
- HUH?

521
00:21:56,857 --> 00:21:58,024
- [BOING BOING]

522
00:21:58,057 --> 00:22:00,357
YOU WON'T GET AWAY WITH THIS!

523
00:22:00,390 --> 00:22:01,590
- [MEOWING]

524
00:22:01,624 --> 00:22:02,424
- RUN!

525
00:22:02,457 --> 00:22:04,457
RUN FOR MY LIFE!

526
00:22:05,924 --> 00:22:07,457
- COME BACK HERE!

527
00:22:07,490 --> 00:22:09,590
- WHEN IT COMES TO FLEEING,

528
00:22:09,624 --> 00:22:12,724
MYOGA IS DEFINITELY THE BEST.

529
00:22:12,757 --> 00:22:14,224
- [ALL SIGH]

530
00:22:14,257 --> 00:22:16,590
- STOP, MYOGA!

531
00:22:16,624 --> 00:22:18,424
- NO WAY!

532
00:22:25,238 --> 00:22:28,005
- [SINGING IN JAPANESE]

533
00:23:59,038 --> 00:24:02,471
- INUYASHA, CAN'T YOU FIND
NARAKU'S CASTLE YET?

534
00:24:02,505 --> 00:24:03,405
- STOP YAKKING.

535
00:24:03,438 --> 00:24:04,738
I CAN'T CONCENTRATE.

536
00:24:04,771 --> 00:24:05,871
- TONIGHT'S THE NEW MOON.

537
00:24:05,905 --> 00:24:07,971
HAVE YOU LOST YOUR
SENSE OF SMELL?

538
00:24:08,005 --> 00:24:09,971
- YOU WISH.

539
00:24:10,005 --> 00:24:10,771
I KNOW THIS SCENT.

540
00:24:10,805 --> 00:24:13,171
IT'S KOGA OF
THE WOLF DEMON TRIBE.

541
00:24:13,205 --> 00:24:14,871
- THAT'S THE LEAST
OF OUR WORRIES.

542
00:24:14,905 --> 00:24:17,271
KAGURA IS MAKING A DEAL
WITH SESSHOMARU.

543
00:24:17,305 --> 00:24:22,171
- NEXT TIME, "NARAKU'S BARRIER,
KAGURA'S DECISION."

544
00:24:22,205 --> 00:24:23,005
DAMN!

545
00:24:23,038 --> 00:24:24,038
OF ALL THE TIMES!

